scopecontent.p:
Series X consists of two films in Spanish. The first film is about alcoholism, drug addiction, and use of tobacco. The second film is about a program for UMC women taken from a book (
               Mujeres Forjando un Mundo
            ) that centers on how women face change and cope with it.

did.unittitle:
"South Africa Report" ("South Africa Now," 
                           Newsreel One
                        ); This film is about intimidation by police in South Africa against native Africans, such as the police imprisoning and abusing teenage boys. This film is also about peaceful protest against the violence. (VHS)
